941
00:43:18,639 --> 00:43:22,739
[SPEAKER_01] a mogli bi se koristiti da neki način smo više malo to upoznati.

942
00:43:22,739 --> 00:43:25,679
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže ovako, mi uvijek izgovaramo,

943
00:43:25,880 --> 00:43:27,519
[SPEAKER_01] tvoju smrt gospodina vješujemo,

944
00:43:27,519 --> 00:43:29,239
[SPEAKER_01] tvoje uskrasnuće slavimo,

945
00:43:29,239 --> 00:43:30,739
[SPEAKER_01] tvoji slavni dolazak i šekujemo.

946
00:43:30,739 --> 00:43:31,500
[SPEAKER_01] To uvijek govorimo.

947
00:43:31,500 --> 00:43:35,539
[SPEAKER_01] A postoješ dvije mogućnosti koje nismo nikada upotrijebili.

948
00:43:35,539 --> 00:43:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] A to kaže,

949
00:43:37,199 --> 00:43:39,880
[SPEAKER_01] Kad god blagujemo ovaj kruh i pijemo kaleš,

950
00:43:39,880 --> 00:43:42,139
[SPEAKER_01] tvoju smrt gospodina vještamo,

951
00:43:42,139 --> 00:43:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] tvoj slavni dolazak i šekujemo.

952
00:43:44,000 --> 00:43:45,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ili treća molitva,

953
00:43:45,800 --> 00:43:48,360
[SPEAKER_01] spasi nas spasitelju svijeta,

954
00:43:48,360 --> 00:43:52,579
[SPEAKER_01] koji si nas svojim križem i uskrasnućem oslobodio.

955
00:43:52,579 --> 00:43:56,480
[SPEAKER_01] Sada kada je mogućnost raznih formulacija,

956
00:43:56,480 --> 00:44:00,179
[SPEAKER_01] koje se, barem kod nas u Hrvatskoj, nikada ne koriste.

957
00:44:00,179 --> 00:44:01,780
[SPEAKER_01] A postoje u ovoj knjizi.

958
00:44:01,780 --> 00:44:03,840
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto je to ikon napisao?

959
00:44:03,840 --> 00:44:06,619
[SPEAKER_01] To su prekraste molite prošlosti,

960
00:44:07,199 --> 00:44:08,940
[SPEAKER_01] koje su ušli da daje način liturgiju,

961
00:44:08,940 --> 00:44:11,039
[SPEAKER_01] ali se ne koriste.

962
00:44:11,039 --> 00:44:15,159
[SPEAKER_01] Da smo proveli ovaj članak liturgijske reforme,

963
00:44:15,159 --> 00:44:19,960
[SPEAKER_01] bio bi onda jedan karizmatski žamor u crkvi,

964
00:44:19,960 --> 00:44:21,820
[SPEAKER_01] tako ću da je to nekako nazvati.

965
00:44:21,820 --> 00:44:24,260
[SPEAKER_01] Neko bi rekao, tvoju spravo gospodina vještamo,

966
00:44:24,260 --> 00:44:26,880
[SPEAKER_01] drugi bi rekao, da kad god blagujemo ovaj kruh,

967
00:44:26,880 --> 00:44:29,820
[SPEAKER_01] teće bi govorio, spasi nas, spasiti svijeta.

968
00:44:29,820 --> 00:44:33,619
[SPEAKER_01] Sada bi nešto govorio i crkva bi bila jako karizmatska,

969
00:44:33,619 --> 00:44:36,300
[SPEAKER_01] ali to nismo prepoznali kao jednu kvalitetu,

970
00:44:36,360 --> 00:44:37,360
[SPEAKER_01] pa osim tu gdje i jesmo.

971
00:44:37,360 --> 00:44:42,699
[SPEAKER_01] U koris karizmatika, dakle bi to išlo na taj način,

972
00:44:42,699 --> 00:44:45,940
[SPEAKER_01] ali liturgija dopušta da malo žamori u crkvi,

973
00:44:45,940 --> 00:44:48,219
[SPEAKER_01] da svako kaže svoje kako si ječali.

974
00:44:48,219 --> 00:44:52,260
[SPEAKER_01] Osjetiti to bilo crkve,

975
00:44:52,260 --> 00:44:54,300
[SPEAKER_01] crkve je jedan živi organizam,

976
00:44:54,300 --> 00:44:55,539
[SPEAKER_01] nije to nešto mrtvo,

977
00:44:55,539 --> 00:44:59,219
[SPEAKER_01] nego naći svoje mjesto u toj cijelom događanju.

978
00:44:59,860 --> 00:45:02,320
[SPEAKER_01] Konstantino preokret, car Konstantin,

979
00:45:02,320 --> 00:45:04,199
[SPEAKER_01] daje tu slobodu u kršćanima

980
00:45:04,199 --> 00:45:08,280
[SPEAKER_01] i onda počinje to odvajanje istočne i zapadne liturgije.

981
00:45:08,280 --> 00:45:09,860
[SPEAKER_01] Svako nekako po svome,

982
00:45:09,860 --> 00:45:11,920
[SPEAKER_01] teško je dodoći nekak jedinstva,

983
00:45:11,920 --> 00:45:14,539
[SPEAKER_01] a opet danas gledamo to kao bogatstvo crkve.

984
00:45:15,619 --> 00:45:18,440
[SPEAKER_01] Mi imamo takozvani i zagrebački obret,

985
00:45:18,440 --> 00:45:19,619
[SPEAKER_01] zagrebačku muku,

986
00:45:19,619 --> 00:45:22,260
[SPEAKER_01] možemo se ponositi tim obredom,

987
00:45:22,260 --> 00:45:25,079
[SPEAKER_01] to pjevamo na veliki petak u našoj crkvi,

988
00:45:25,079 --> 00:45:26,980
[SPEAKER_01] zagrebački obret Ivanove muke,

989
00:45:26,980 --> 00:45:29,780
[SPEAKER_01] muke isto je po Ivanu,

990
00:45:29,780 --> 00:45:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] a posto je recimo ambrozijanski obret,

991
00:45:33,000 --> 00:45:36,780
[SPEAKER_01] koji je durače na liturgijska crkve, sve ostalo.

992
00:45:36,780 --> 00:45:39,679
[SPEAKER_01] Zatim imamo stvaranje liturgijskih obitelji,

993
00:45:39,679 --> 00:45:40,719
[SPEAKER_01] na isto koji zapadu,

994
00:45:40,719 --> 00:45:43,500
[SPEAKER_01] Papa Gregor VII je strogi papa

995
00:45:43,500 --> 00:45:47,059
[SPEAKER_01] i on uvodi red u zapadnu crkvu.

996
00:45:47,059 --> 00:45:48,619
[SPEAKER_01] Svi moraju isto moliti

997
00:45:48,619 --> 00:45:51,059
[SPEAKER_01] i nema tu sad više šale

998
00:45:51,059 --> 00:45:52,159
[SPEAKER_01] za nekako drugačije,

999
00:45:52,159 --> 00:45:54,219
[SPEAKER_01] nego svi imaju strogi rimski obret.

1000
00:45:54,219 --> 00:45:56,860
[SPEAKER_01] To je papa koji je uveo celibat u crkvu,

1001
00:45:56,860 --> 00:45:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, kaže mogu ja, mogu svi,

1002
00:45:58,960 --> 00:46:00,519
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, tako je prolazio celibat,

1003
00:46:00,519 --> 00:46:01,039
[SPEAKER_01] je li, dakle,

1004
00:46:01,039 --> 00:46:02,639
[SPEAKER_01] i na to ne načeli.

1005
00:46:02,639 --> 00:46:04,900
[SPEAKER_01] Onda imamo

1006
00:46:04,900 --> 00:46:08,019
[SPEAKER_01] trintijska reforma,

1007
00:46:08,019 --> 00:46:11,280
[SPEAKER_01] znači protestanti ruše svetu misu,

1008
00:46:11,280 --> 00:46:14,739
[SPEAKER_01] u smislu da mi ponovno Isusa razapinjimo.

1009
00:46:14,739 --> 00:46:17,739
[SPEAKER_01] Pa onda reforma koncila reka,

1010
00:46:17,739 --> 00:46:18,599
[SPEAKER_01] nije to razapinjenje,

1011
00:46:18,599 --> 00:46:20,679
[SPEAKER_01] nego je to uprisutnjenje

1012
00:46:20,679 --> 00:46:22,840
[SPEAKER_01] Isusa ponovno u našu povijeseri.

1013
00:46:22,840 --> 00:46:25,340
[SPEAKER_01] I ova reforma koju danas govorimo

1014
00:46:25,340 --> 00:46:26,519
[SPEAKER_01] o Vatikanskog sabora,

1015
00:46:27,019 --> 00:46:29,139
[SPEAKER_01] znači, od 16. stoljeća,

1016
00:46:29,139 --> 00:46:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] 1563. od kada završava trintijski koncil,

1017
00:46:33,539 --> 00:46:40,380
[SPEAKER_01] do 1963. se liturgija služi na isti način.

1018
00:46:40,380 --> 00:46:42,219
[SPEAKER_01] Oltar prema istoku,

1019
00:46:42,219 --> 00:46:43,960
[SPEAKER_01] svećenik na žrtveniku,

1020
00:46:43,960 --> 00:46:45,699
[SPEAKER_01] i slavi liturgije.

1021
00:46:45,699 --> 00:46:47,360
[SPEAKER_01] 4. stoljeća se nije ništa

1022
00:46:47,360 --> 00:46:48,760
[SPEAKER_01] u crkvi mijenjalo.

1023
00:46:48,760 --> 00:46:51,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pokušalo se mijenjati prvi Vatikanskim,

1024
00:46:51,960 --> 00:46:52,380
[SPEAKER_01] ali rekao sam,

1025
00:46:52,380 --> 00:46:53,099
[SPEAKER_01] on je prekinut,

1026
00:46:53,099 --> 00:46:54,719
[SPEAKER_01] pa se nije dalje nastavio.

1027
00:46:54,719 --> 00:46:56,880
[SPEAKER_01] I onda smo čekali

1028
00:46:56,880 --> 00:46:59,760
[SPEAKER_01] 1963. godina,

1029
00:46:59,760 --> 00:47:00,960
[SPEAKER_01] dođemo do ovog dokumenta

1030
00:47:00,960 --> 00:47:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] o liturgiji crkve,

1031
00:47:02,539 --> 00:47:05,159
[SPEAKER_01] da bi se taj dio promijenio.

1032
00:47:05,880 --> 00:47:07,059
[SPEAKER_01] Pazite, mislite na latinskome,

1033
00:47:07,059 --> 00:47:08,300
[SPEAKER_01] ništa ne razumiješ,

1034
00:47:08,300 --> 00:47:09,619
[SPEAKER_01] obredi nije jasan.

1035
00:47:09,619 --> 00:47:11,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ko će biti na misli, dakle?

1036
00:47:11,639 --> 00:47:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] Predosadno.

1037
00:47:12,460 --> 00:47:13,960
[SPEAKER_01] Crkva prepozna,

1038
00:47:13,960 --> 00:47:16,260
[SPEAKER_01] treba liturgiju približiti narod.

1039
00:47:16,260 --> 00:47:17,880
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala Bogu da mi živimo

1040
00:47:17,880 --> 00:47:18,840
[SPEAKER_01] u tim vremenima

1041
00:47:18,840 --> 00:47:20,840
[SPEAKER_01] u koje crkva mijenja.

1042
00:47:20,840 --> 00:47:22,559
[SPEAKER_01] Vidite, crkva ima vlast.

1043
00:47:22,559 --> 00:47:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je jedan povijesni presjek,

1044
00:47:24,659 --> 00:47:25,559
[SPEAKER_01] kratki presjek,

1045
00:47:25,559 --> 00:47:27,440
[SPEAKER_01] da mijenja liturgiju.

1046
00:47:27,440 --> 00:47:29,559
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ne mijenja se bit.

1047
00:47:29,559 --> 00:47:32,119
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek ostaje navještaj Bože riječi,

1048
00:47:32,119 --> 00:47:34,039
[SPEAKER_01] starog, novog zavjeta

1049
00:47:34,039 --> 00:47:35,519
[SPEAKER_01] i Euharistija.

1050
00:47:36,039 --> 00:47:38,099
[SPEAKER_01] Odnosno, prinos darova kao takvi.

1051
00:47:38,099 --> 00:47:39,739
[SPEAKER_01] Darovi se prinose,

1052
00:47:39,739 --> 00:47:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] to je u svim liturgijama.

1053
00:47:42,000 --> 00:47:43,320
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, istočnim, zapadnima,

1054
00:47:43,320 --> 00:47:44,880
[SPEAKER_01] kroz cijelu povijest,

1055
00:47:44,880 --> 00:47:45,940
[SPEAKER_01] to se ne mijenja.

1056
00:47:45,940 --> 00:47:47,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je tijelo moje,

1057
00:47:47,139 --> 00:47:47,980
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je krv moja,

1058
00:47:47,980 --> 00:47:49,300
[SPEAKER_01] to je, nema promjene.

1059
00:47:49,300 --> 00:47:50,400
[SPEAKER_01] Inče, nema Euharistije.

1060
00:47:50,400 --> 00:47:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] A sad, da li ćemo se križati

1061
00:47:53,000 --> 00:47:54,480
[SPEAKER_01] sa tri prsta, pet prstiju,

1062
00:47:54,480 --> 00:47:55,860
[SPEAKER_01] hoćemo se nakloniti,

1063
00:47:55,860 --> 00:47:57,460
[SPEAKER_01] hoćemo, to je stvar liturgije,

1064
00:47:57,460 --> 00:47:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno liturgičara,

1065
00:47:58,739 --> 00:48:00,579
[SPEAKER_01] kako će oni to objasniti?

1066
00:48:00,579 --> 00:48:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] Da narodu bude što jasnije

1067
00:48:02,460 --> 00:48:03,920
[SPEAKER_01] i što bliže ta crkva.

1068
00:48:03,960 --> 00:48:06,219
[SPEAKER_01] Da se ne svađamo, da li li sa tri, pet prstiju se križamo,

1069
00:48:06,219 --> 00:48:07,699
[SPEAKER_01] jer to je manje bitno, dakle.

1070
00:48:07,699 --> 00:48:08,719
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, bitno se križamo.

1071
00:48:08,719 --> 00:48:10,360
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, sad ovaj.

1072
00:48:10,360 --> 00:48:13,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kad smo u duhu te liturgije,

1073
00:48:13,860 --> 00:48:15,300
[SPEAKER_01] onda to razumijemo.

1074
00:48:15,300 --> 00:48:17,719
[SPEAKER_01] Manje bitno ta forma,

1075
00:48:17,719 --> 00:48:19,340
[SPEAKER_01] bitno ima bit.

1076
00:48:19,340 --> 00:48:20,900
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, sve liturgije,

1077
00:48:20,900 --> 00:48:21,980
[SPEAKER_01] svih vremena,

1078
00:48:21,980 --> 00:48:23,480
[SPEAKER_01] svih prostora imaju

1079
00:48:23,480 --> 00:48:25,059
[SPEAKER_01] Euharistiju,

1080
00:48:25,059 --> 00:48:26,440
[SPEAKER_01] u spislu pretvorbe,

1081
00:48:26,440 --> 00:48:29,139
[SPEAKER_01] i, znači, prinos darova pa pretvorba,

1082
00:48:29,539 --> 00:48:31,320
[SPEAKER_01] i prije toga slušanje Bože riječi,

1083
00:48:31,320 --> 00:48:32,539
[SPEAKER_01] razmatljanje toj riječi.

1084
00:48:32,539 --> 00:48:33,380
[SPEAKER_01] To imaju svi.

1085
00:48:33,380 --> 00:48:35,219
[SPEAKER_01] Detalje su onda manje,

1086
00:48:35,219 --> 00:48:36,239
[SPEAKER_01] tu je nejako bitne.

1087
00:48:36,239 --> 00:48:37,300
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro?

1088
00:48:37,300 --> 00:48:40,300
[SPEAKER_01] Liturgijski jezik.

1089
00:48:40,300 --> 00:48:42,400
[SPEAKER_01] Zato vam možemo poslužiti,

1090
00:48:42,400 --> 00:48:45,440
[SPEAKER_01] ova knjižica, već kakve lijepa,

1091
00:48:45,440 --> 00:48:47,119
[SPEAKER_01] mali liturgijski leksikon, dakle.

1092
00:48:47,119 --> 00:48:49,880
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ćeš naučiti kako se crkva izražava,

1093
00:48:49,880 --> 00:48:50,920
[SPEAKER_01] što ona tu govori,

1094
00:48:50,920 --> 00:48:53,880
[SPEAKER_01] što znači litanije,

1095
00:48:53,880 --> 00:48:56,079
[SPEAKER_01] što znači prepošto,

1096
00:48:56,079 --> 00:48:58,440
[SPEAKER_01] prezbiteri, tako dalje, tako sve stvari.

1097
00:48:58,440 --> 00:49:00,460
[SPEAKER_01] To ćeš znaći u ovoj knjižici,

1098
00:49:00,460 --> 00:49:02,420
[SPEAKER_01] ima ih na stotine raznih vrsta,

1099
00:49:02,420 --> 00:49:04,260
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj možemo jedan praktični,

1100
00:49:04,260 --> 00:49:06,460
[SPEAKER_01] mali, za najosnovnije stvari,

1101
00:49:06,460 --> 00:49:09,760
[SPEAKER_01] upoznati što to crkva misli,

1102
00:49:09,760 --> 00:49:11,059
[SPEAKER_01] kad kaže tu neku riječ,

1103
00:49:11,059 --> 00:49:12,980
[SPEAKER_01] što ona u sebi to uključuje.

1104
00:49:12,980 --> 00:49:15,760
[SPEAKER_01] Govorili turitski znakova.

1105
00:49:16,659 --> 00:49:18,480
[SPEAKER_01] Imate poznatu jednu knjižicu,

1106
00:49:18,480 --> 00:49:19,599
[SPEAKER_01] Romano o Gvardini,

1107
00:49:19,599 --> 00:49:21,280
[SPEAKER_01] gdje on objašnjava,

1108
00:49:21,280 --> 00:49:23,340
[SPEAKER_01] isto je u zdanju KS-a,

1109
00:49:23,340 --> 00:49:24,760
[SPEAKER_01] kršćanske sadošnje,

1110
00:49:24,760 --> 00:49:26,280
[SPEAKER_01] ruke, što znači,

1111
00:49:26,280 --> 00:49:27,380
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam vam tražio knjivu,

1112
00:49:27,380 --> 00:49:28,059
[SPEAKER_01] nisam uspio odnaš,

1113
00:49:28,059 --> 00:49:29,480
[SPEAKER_01] pa nemam joj ovdje da pokažem,

1114
00:49:29,480 --> 00:49:31,360
[SPEAKER_01] ali je ovako vrlo zgodna,

1115
00:49:31,360 --> 00:49:32,900
[SPEAKER_01] negdje mi se je pogubila,

1116
00:49:32,900 --> 00:49:33,559
[SPEAKER_01] da ne znam gdje je.

1117
00:49:33,559 --> 00:49:38,260
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje objašnjava što znači ruke u liturgiji,

1118
00:49:38,260 --> 00:49:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] što znači pokleknuti, prostracija,

1119
00:49:41,079 --> 00:49:42,500
[SPEAKER_01] znači sve te pokrete,

1120
00:49:42,500 --> 00:49:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] da nam bude liturgija jasna.

1121
00:49:45,000 --> 00:49:46,880
[SPEAKER_01] Što ćete iti češće na misu,

1122
00:49:46,880 --> 00:49:48,119
[SPEAKER_01] to ćete više razumijeti,

1123
00:49:48,119 --> 00:49:49,639
[SPEAKER_01] dakle to je tako jednostavno pravilo,

1124
00:49:49,639 --> 00:49:52,059
[SPEAKER_01] ali možemo neke stvari naučiti bolje.

1125
00:49:52,059 --> 00:49:54,780
[SPEAKER_01] Današnja sposobnost za liturgiju,

1126
00:49:54,780 --> 00:49:56,199
[SPEAKER_01] glazba u bogoslužju,

1127
00:49:56,199 --> 00:50:01,980
[SPEAKER_01] karizmatski duh je nama drag i lijep,

1128
00:50:01,980 --> 00:50:08,579
[SPEAKER_01] ali on neki način razbija liturgiju.

1129
00:50:10,039 --> 00:50:12,719
[SPEAKER_01] To je, da razumijete, prigovor liturgičara,

1130
00:50:12,719 --> 00:50:16,219
[SPEAKER_01] zašto ne karizmatsko slavlje na sve toj misi?

1131
00:50:16,219 --> 00:50:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer misa smiruje, ona mir unosi.

1132
00:50:21,000 --> 00:50:23,699
[SPEAKER_01] Nama je lijepo na karizmatskoj zajednici,

1133
00:50:23,699 --> 00:50:24,420
[SPEAKER_01] da se razumijemo,

1134
00:50:24,420 --> 00:50:28,360
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo, malo prihvatimo tu jednu prilagodbu

1135
00:50:28,360 --> 00:50:30,539
[SPEAKER_01] i da shvatimo zbog čega je to.

1136
00:50:30,539 --> 00:50:33,500
[SPEAKER_01] Misa umiruje.

1137
00:50:33,500 --> 00:50:35,599
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je bit.

1138
00:50:35,599 --> 00:50:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da smiri, a ne da ti duhu zburka

1139
00:50:39,000 --> 00:50:40,980
[SPEAKER_01] kao što radi karizmatski duh,

1140
00:50:40,980 --> 00:50:42,320
[SPEAKER_01] sa svojim pjesama,

1141
00:50:42,320 --> 00:50:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] pa evo, tu tražimo, daj Bož,

1142
00:50:44,000 --> 00:50:45,579
[SPEAKER_01] da nam se te stvari jako poslože

1143
00:50:45,579 --> 00:50:48,940
[SPEAKER_01] i da možemo naći nekakvi zajednički jezik,

1144
00:50:48,940 --> 00:50:51,380
[SPEAKER_01] pa da i znamo i za plesati.

1145
00:50:51,380 --> 00:50:53,679
[SPEAKER_01] To je problem, recimo imate danas u Africi,

1146
00:50:53,679 --> 00:50:56,880
[SPEAKER_01] kažu kršari iz Afrike,

1147
00:50:57,179 --> 00:50:59,179
[SPEAKER_01] a što je s nama, mi na misi plešemo,

1148
00:50:59,179 --> 00:51:02,719
[SPEAKER_01] sve moguće, tri sata traje misa nikak kraja,

1149
00:51:02,719 --> 00:51:04,280
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, prinos darova,

1150
00:51:04,280 --> 00:51:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] to ti je, nose žive životinja pred odara.

1151
00:51:07,000 --> 00:51:09,539
[SPEAKER_01] Isto je katovička liturgija,

1152
00:51:09,539 --> 00:51:11,119
[SPEAKER_01] kao ovako od nas je, dakle.

1153
00:51:11,119 --> 00:51:14,280
[SPEAKER_01] Tada, teško da se sve to uslariti,

1154
00:51:14,280 --> 00:51:16,059
[SPEAKER_01] ali kad razumijemo bit,

1155
00:51:16,059 --> 00:51:18,019
[SPEAKER_01] da je to davanje svog vremena,

1156
00:51:18,019 --> 00:51:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] svojih dobara Bogu,

1157
00:51:20,079 --> 00:51:22,260
[SPEAKER_01] onda može biti na misi tri sata.

1158
00:51:22,699 --> 00:51:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] Papinska misa traje tri sata

1159
00:51:24,380 --> 00:51:25,940
[SPEAKER_01] i niko s nje ne bježi.

1160
00:51:25,940 --> 00:51:28,780
[SPEAKER_01] Jer je to papinska misa.

1161
00:51:28,780 --> 00:51:31,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ima svoju jednu težinu, ljepotu,

1162
00:51:31,019 --> 00:51:35,099
[SPEAKER_01] teče, znači, jedan tijek liturgije.

1163
00:51:35,099 --> 00:51:38,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što je temeljno pravilno za sve liturgije,

1164
00:51:38,619 --> 00:51:41,699
[SPEAKER_01] u crkvi nemojte nikada žuriti.

1165
00:51:41,699 --> 00:51:45,400
[SPEAKER_01] Crkva je, prema vješnosti, usmjerena.

1166
00:51:45,400 --> 00:51:49,380
[SPEAKER_01] Trčanje po crkvi, nemerni duh,

1167
00:51:49,380 --> 00:51:51,579
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, to nije duh crkve.

1168
00:51:52,059 --> 00:51:54,280
[SPEAKER_01] duh crkve je uvijek tišina,

1169
00:51:54,280 --> 00:51:56,219
[SPEAKER_01] mir, osuškivanje,

1170
00:51:56,219 --> 00:51:57,880
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, jedan

1171
00:51:57,880 --> 00:52:01,019
[SPEAKER_01] duboki taj naklon, dakle, Bogu.

1172
00:52:01,019 --> 00:52:03,340
[SPEAKER_01] To je liturgijski govor.

1173
00:52:03,340 --> 00:52:05,440
[SPEAKER_01] Mi ćemo dalje, kada je maski,

1174
00:52:05,440 --> 00:52:06,420
[SPEAKER_01] nastaviti naše slavlje,

1175
00:52:06,420 --> 00:52:07,059
[SPEAKER_01] da se razumije,

1176
00:52:07,059 --> 00:52:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] ali ćemo poštivati, dakle,

1177
00:52:08,619 --> 00:52:10,719
[SPEAKER_01] i liturgijske, onda, malo propise.

1178
00:52:10,719 --> 00:52:14,039
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, jedan kopski obred.

1179
00:52:14,039 --> 00:52:15,900
[SPEAKER_01] Vedite, svečenika,

1180
00:52:15,900 --> 00:52:17,219
[SPEAKER_01] kako ima u dijelo,

1181
00:52:17,219 --> 00:52:20,440
[SPEAKER_01] obredi koji na razne načine,

1182
00:52:20,440 --> 00:52:21,659
[SPEAKER_01] koji stave ovo tajstvo,

1183
00:52:21,659 --> 00:52:22,539
[SPEAKER_01] o čemu smo govorili.

1184
00:52:22,539 --> 00:52:24,500
[SPEAKER_01] Dalje, imam tu,

1185
00:52:24,500 --> 00:52:25,360
[SPEAKER_01] bizanski obred,

1186
00:52:25,360 --> 00:52:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] to je naš grekokatolički obred,

1187
00:52:28,260 --> 00:52:29,059
[SPEAKER_01] najbliži,

1188
00:52:29,059 --> 00:52:30,519
[SPEAKER_01] tu ga nekako razumijemo.

1189
00:52:30,519 --> 00:52:32,840
[SPEAKER_01] Imate, ispred otara je ikonostas,

1190
00:52:32,840 --> 00:52:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] znači, to je zid koji je oboja

1191
00:52:35,960 --> 00:52:37,059
[SPEAKER_01] sa raznim svecima,

1192
00:52:37,059 --> 00:52:38,139
[SPEAKER_01] naslikan,

1193
00:52:38,139 --> 00:52:39,420
[SPEAKER_01] bogatstvo, dakle,

1194
00:52:39,420 --> 00:52:41,519
[SPEAKER_01] crkva se mjeri bogatstvo

1195
00:52:41,519 --> 00:52:43,300
[SPEAKER_01] po ikonostasu u istočnoj crkvi,

1196
00:52:43,300 --> 00:52:45,280
[SPEAKER_01] tako da je jedno veliko bogatstvo,

1197
00:52:45,280 --> 00:52:46,079
[SPEAKER_01] zato može naći.

1198
00:52:46,800 --> 00:52:47,099
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

1199
00:52:47,099 --> 00:52:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ambrozijanski obred,

1200
00:52:49,539 --> 00:52:51,260
[SPEAKER_01] znači, crkva u Milanu,

1201
00:52:51,260 --> 00:52:52,800
[SPEAKER_01] po nadbiskupu Ambrozijima,

1202
00:52:52,800 --> 00:52:53,579
[SPEAKER_01] svoj obred,

1203
00:52:53,579 --> 00:52:56,300
[SPEAKER_01] koji je danas još uvijek u upotrebi,

1204
00:52:56,300 --> 00:52:57,920
[SPEAKER_01] predi regija,

1205
00:52:57,920 --> 00:53:01,500
[SPEAKER_01] moramo to objasniti zbog čega, dakle.

1206
00:53:02,039 --> 00:53:03,679
[SPEAKER_01] jer je pavao šesti

1207
00:53:03,679 --> 00:53:06,360
[SPEAKER_01] bio milanski nadbiskup, dakle.

1208
00:53:06,360 --> 00:53:07,840
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je onda dao predvilegu se

1209
00:53:07,840 --> 00:53:08,639
[SPEAKER_01] da je obred dađe vrši,

1210
00:53:08,639 --> 00:53:10,219
[SPEAKER_01] kad je postao papa pavao šesti,

1211
00:53:10,219 --> 00:53:11,480
[SPEAKER_01] Giovanni Montini,

1212
00:53:11,480 --> 00:53:13,500
[SPEAKER_01] pa kaže, pa ipak će moja crkva

1213
00:53:13,500 --> 00:53:15,840
[SPEAKER_01] imati pravo još malo svoj obred vršiti,

1214
00:53:15,840 --> 00:53:16,099
[SPEAKER_01] jel'i?

1215
00:53:16,099 --> 00:53:17,400
[SPEAKER_01] A tako, ljudi smo svi,

1216
00:53:17,400 --> 00:53:18,880
[SPEAKER_01] pa i papa pavao šesti, jel'i?

1217
00:53:18,880 --> 00:53:21,420
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, dopustio je da se u milanskoj crkvi

1218
00:53:21,420 --> 00:53:23,460
[SPEAKER_01] vrši milanski ambrozijanski obred,

1219
00:53:23,460 --> 00:53:25,579
[SPEAKER_01] jer je on bio nekada biskup te crkve,

1220
00:53:25,579 --> 00:53:26,519
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, a posto je papa,

1221
00:53:26,519 --> 00:53:27,179
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, vidiš.

1222
00:53:27,179 --> 00:53:29,039
[SPEAKER_01] To je ti jedno sam zaobjasniti,

1223
00:53:29,039 --> 00:53:30,059
[SPEAKER_01] tu crkvi, nije da komuniciralo.

1224
00:53:30,059 --> 00:53:33,139
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, dalje.

1225
00:53:33,139 --> 00:53:34,599
[SPEAKER_01] Tritijski obred,

1226
00:53:34,599 --> 00:53:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] to je ta misel koje sam govorio

1227
00:53:35,960 --> 00:53:37,159
[SPEAKER_01] prije od trijenta,

1228
00:53:37,159 --> 00:53:38,760
[SPEAKER_01] tako je svečnik izgledo kod oltara.

1229
00:53:38,760 --> 00:53:41,039
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja bih sad da biti ovdje,

1230
00:53:41,039 --> 00:53:43,400
[SPEAKER_01] služila oltar,

1231
00:53:43,400 --> 00:53:45,420
[SPEAKER_01] da se služi misel.

1232
00:53:45,420 --> 00:53:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vidite, to je,

1233
00:53:46,000 --> 00:53:47,340
[SPEAKER_01] ne, to su stare crkve,

1234
00:53:47,340 --> 00:53:48,760
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je stari oltarore,

1235
00:53:48,760 --> 00:53:50,059
[SPEAKER_01] koji vidite u starim crkvama,

1236
00:53:50,059 --> 00:53:51,260
[SPEAKER_01] imate dva oltara,

1237
00:53:51,260 --> 00:53:52,559
[SPEAKER_01] če jedan ovakav,

1238
00:53:52,880 --> 00:53:53,619
[SPEAKER_01] a drugi je ovakav,

1239
00:53:53,619 --> 00:53:54,800
[SPEAKER_01] tako je svečnik služio misu.

1240
00:53:54,800 --> 00:53:58,019
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je bilo naš zapadni obred

1241
00:53:58,019 --> 00:54:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] služenja sve te mise.

1242
00:54:00,000 --> 00:54:01,440
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

1243
00:54:01,440 --> 00:54:04,800
[SPEAKER_01] E sad, to ćemo se polako privesti

1244
00:54:04,800 --> 00:54:05,539
[SPEAKER_01] svar kraju.

1245
00:54:05,539 --> 00:54:07,099
[SPEAKER_01] Još možda koja knjiga.

1246
00:54:07,099 --> 00:54:11,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam zarijski svečnik,

1247
00:54:11,320 --> 00:54:12,280
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, šta ću...

1248
00:54:12,280 --> 00:54:14,659
[SPEAKER_01] Leksikon, ikonografija,

1249
00:54:14,659 --> 00:54:16,940
[SPEAKER_01] liturke simbolike zapadnog crkčanstva,

1250
00:54:16,940 --> 00:54:18,159
[SPEAKER_01] znači, da razumiješ

1251
00:54:18,159 --> 00:54:20,119
[SPEAKER_01] ovo što sam ja sam sve nekako govorio,

1252
00:54:20,119 --> 00:54:21,380
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje ti piše,

1253
00:54:21,380 --> 00:54:22,340
[SPEAKER_01] u knjizi se piše,

1254
00:54:22,780 --> 00:54:23,719
[SPEAKER_01] da razumiješ tu knjigu.

1255
00:54:23,719 --> 00:54:27,039
[SPEAKER_01] Da razumiješ istočnu crkvi,

1256
00:54:27,039 --> 00:54:27,880
[SPEAKER_01] imaš ovu knjigu,

1257
00:54:27,880 --> 00:54:28,280
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1258
00:54:28,280 --> 00:54:30,420
[SPEAKER_01] duh i život,

1259
00:54:30,420 --> 00:54:31,340
[SPEAKER_01] istočne crkve,

1260
00:54:31,340 --> 00:54:31,579
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1261
00:54:31,579 --> 00:54:32,739
[SPEAKER_01] kako oni funkcioniraju,

1262
00:54:32,739 --> 00:54:33,079
[SPEAKER_01] dakle.

1263
00:54:33,079 --> 00:54:36,159
[SPEAKER_01] Pa onda imaš od naša crkva Zagorca,

1264
00:54:36,159 --> 00:54:37,760
[SPEAKER_01] Kristova otajstva,

1265
00:54:37,760 --> 00:54:38,059
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1266
00:54:38,059 --> 00:54:38,380
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1267
00:54:38,380 --> 00:54:39,940
[SPEAKER_01] sve od jehoj objašira isto.

1268
00:54:45,940 --> 00:54:48,500
[SPEAKER_01] Euharistija je u životu crkve kroz povijest,

1269
00:54:48,500 --> 00:54:50,320
[SPEAKER_01] naš teolog na koncilu,

1270
00:54:50,400 --> 00:54:51,659
[SPEAKER_01] pater Šagibunić,

1271
00:54:51,659 --> 00:54:53,019
[SPEAKER_01] Kapucin, dakle,

1272
00:54:53,019 --> 00:54:53,639
[SPEAKER_01] je poznati,

1273
00:54:53,639 --> 00:54:56,360
[SPEAKER_01] koji je pratio kredinalna šepera na koncilu,

1274
00:54:56,360 --> 00:54:57,719
[SPEAKER_01] pa evo,

1275
00:54:57,719 --> 00:54:58,780
[SPEAKER_01] on je napisao puno lijepih,

1276
00:54:58,780 --> 00:54:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] krasih knjiga,

1277
00:54:59,619 --> 00:55:04,179
[SPEAKER_01] bio je ovako vrlo duhovi profesor,

1278
00:55:04,179 --> 00:55:05,400
[SPEAKER_01] jednom zgodom,

1279
00:55:05,400 --> 00:55:06,880
[SPEAKER_01] njega je što agiralo,

1280
00:55:07,559 --> 00:55:10,559
[SPEAKER_01] pa još uvijek je predavan na fakultetu,

1281
00:55:10,559 --> 00:55:11,639
[SPEAKER_01] išao je malo sporadje,

1282
00:55:11,639 --> 00:55:14,059
[SPEAKER_01] se je trudio da predaje studentima,

1283
00:55:14,059 --> 00:55:16,579
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo jako uživali na njegovim predavanjima,

1284
00:55:16,579 --> 00:55:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] i dan put on dođe,

1285
00:55:18,039 --> 00:55:21,719
[SPEAKER_01] ha, šta vi mislite o svom profesoru?

1286
00:55:21,719 --> 00:55:23,980
[SPEAKER_01] A moj jedan kolega,

1287
00:55:23,980 --> 00:55:24,980
[SPEAKER_01] koji stopao iz Vali,

1288
00:55:24,980 --> 00:55:25,199
[SPEAKER_01] kaže,

1289
00:55:25,199 --> 00:55:26,820
[SPEAKER_01] profesor, u Brtima sve najbolje.

1290
00:55:26,820 --> 00:55:35,519
[SPEAKER_01] Dalje ćemo nastaviti predavanje.

1291
00:55:37,079 --> 00:55:38,179
[SPEAKER_01] Tako sam ali zrao.

1292
00:55:38,179 --> 00:55:42,199
[SPEAKER_01] Jako šalj, jako duhovit,

1293
00:55:42,199 --> 00:55:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer je puno ti,

1294
00:55:44,000 --> 00:55:45,940
[SPEAKER_01] a inače je vrlo ovako učen čovjek,

1295
00:55:45,940 --> 00:55:47,840
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, bilo uživanca njega slušati,

1296
00:55:47,840 --> 00:55:50,440
[SPEAKER_01] tako smo mi rekao da je o mrtima sve najbolje,

1297
00:55:50,440 --> 00:55:50,880
[SPEAKER_01] pa dakle,

1298
00:55:50,880 --> 00:55:52,960
[SPEAKER_01] evo,

1299
00:55:52,960 --> 00:55:54,840
[SPEAKER_01] sve zrao je došao za tim smjerom.

1300
00:55:54,840 --> 00:55:57,380
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, tako nekako vam ta liturgija govori,

1301
00:55:57,380 --> 00:55:59,099
[SPEAKER_01] što treba tu sve činiti,

1302
00:55:59,099 --> 00:56:01,579
[SPEAKER_01] u ovom dokumentu koji obrađujemo,

1303
00:56:01,579 --> 00:56:03,260
[SPEAKER_01] govori se o općim načelima

1304
00:56:03,260 --> 00:56:04,800
[SPEAKER_01] za obdugu liturgije,

1305
00:56:05,599 --> 00:56:07,159
[SPEAKER_01] trebalo je od nekog krenu, znate.

1306
00:56:07,159 --> 00:56:09,099
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kad imate jednu povijest,

1307
00:56:09,099 --> 00:56:11,039
[SPEAKER_01] staru 500 godina,

1308
00:56:11,039 --> 00:56:11,619
[SPEAKER_01] 400,

1309
00:56:11,619 --> 00:56:13,219
[SPEAKER_01] od Trinitinskog cila,

1310
00:56:13,219 --> 00:56:15,019
[SPEAKER_01] trebalo se imati hrabrost

1311
00:56:15,019 --> 00:56:16,260
[SPEAKER_01] i kako sad to promijeniti.

1312
00:56:16,260 --> 00:56:18,760
[SPEAKER_01] Nije to sad tako moguće

1313
00:56:18,760 --> 00:56:20,239
[SPEAKER_01] preko noći promijeniti.

1314
00:56:20,239 --> 00:56:22,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, 400 godina služi se misar

1315
00:56:22,079 --> 00:56:23,219
[SPEAKER_01] po Trinitinskom obredu,

1316
00:56:23,219 --> 00:56:24,699
[SPEAKER_01] ovod je svečenik, dakle,

1317
00:56:24,699 --> 00:56:26,599
[SPEAKER_01] prema otaru gledali,

1318
00:56:26,599 --> 00:56:28,559
[SPEAKER_01] i za kako to promijeniti.

1319
00:56:28,559 --> 00:56:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] Danas je zasvim drugovite.

1320
00:56:29,960 --> 00:56:31,059
[SPEAKER_01] Gleda se prema narodu,

1321
00:56:31,059 --> 00:56:32,760
[SPEAKER_01] se gleda velike promjene.

1322
00:56:32,760 --> 00:56:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Trebalo imati hrabrosti,

1323
00:56:35,000 --> 00:56:36,500
[SPEAKER_01] stati iza tih promjena.

1324
00:56:36,500 --> 00:56:37,860
[SPEAKER_01] Bez odstavno za koliko ali bile

1325
00:56:37,860 --> 00:56:38,920
[SPEAKER_01] teške, bolne,

1326
00:56:38,920 --> 00:56:40,539
[SPEAKER_01] nekima to je bilo jako teško

1327
00:56:40,539 --> 00:56:42,980
[SPEAKER_01] se rastati od stare liturgije,

1328
00:56:43,619 --> 00:56:44,519
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo, kad gledamo

1329
00:56:44,519 --> 00:56:45,900
[SPEAKER_01] u ovim dokumentima,

1330
00:56:45,900 --> 00:56:48,260
[SPEAKER_01] broj glasača bio je

1331
00:56:48,260 --> 00:56:53,340
[SPEAKER_01] preko 2000 otaca na koncilu,

1332
00:56:53,340 --> 00:56:54,519
[SPEAKER_01] znači biskupa,

1333
00:56:54,519 --> 00:56:58,159
[SPEAKER_01] koji su glasali za te promjene.

1334
00:56:58,159 --> 00:56:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] Stotinjak je bilo uvijek

1335
00:56:59,619 --> 00:57:00,679
[SPEAKER_01] nekakvi kontra,

1336
00:57:00,679 --> 00:57:03,079
[SPEAKER_01] nekakvi starinski možda sloj

1337
00:57:03,079 --> 00:57:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] biskupa koji nije razumije

1338
00:57:04,539 --> 00:57:05,159
[SPEAKER_01] te promjene.

1339
00:57:05,159 --> 00:57:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] Duh sveti puše,

1340
00:57:07,539 --> 00:57:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] znači, i kroz koncilu.

1341
00:57:08,619 --> 00:57:11,119
[SPEAKER_01] To je isto dio crkve.

1342
00:57:11,119 --> 00:57:12,219
[SPEAKER_01] Imate dijela apostolska.

1343
00:57:13,519 --> 00:57:14,760
[SPEAKER_01] prvi koncil u Jeruzalemu.

1344
00:57:14,760 --> 00:57:16,360
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, više nema Isusa.

1345
00:57:16,360 --> 00:57:18,780
[SPEAKER_01] Biskupi se sastaju,

1346
00:57:18,780 --> 00:57:19,420
[SPEAKER_01] apostoli,

1347
00:57:19,420 --> 00:57:21,820
[SPEAKER_01] i moraju nešto odlučiti.

1348
00:57:21,820 --> 00:57:23,619
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je vrlo teško pitanje,

1349
00:57:23,619 --> 00:57:25,260
[SPEAKER_01] a pitanje se sastavilo u tome

1350
00:57:25,260 --> 00:57:25,840
[SPEAKER_01] da li treba

1351
00:57:25,840 --> 00:57:28,179
[SPEAKER_01] one koji nisu bili židovi

1352
00:57:28,179 --> 00:57:31,099
[SPEAKER_01] prvo učiniti židove,

1353
00:57:31,099 --> 00:57:32,420
[SPEAKER_01] a onda kršane.

1354
00:57:32,420 --> 00:57:34,300
[SPEAKER_01] A to znači u prijevodu

1355
00:57:34,300 --> 00:57:35,440
[SPEAKER_01] prvo obrezanje,

1356
00:57:35,440 --> 00:57:36,739
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda kršteinje.

1357
00:57:36,739 --> 00:57:38,599
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo pitanje,

1358
00:57:38,599 --> 00:57:39,800
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo složeno pitanje.

1359
00:57:39,800 --> 00:57:42,519
[SPEAKER_01] Pao je to presjekao svojom vlašu

1360
00:57:42,519 --> 00:57:43,039
[SPEAKER_01] i rekao ne.

1361
00:57:43,420 --> 00:57:44,599
[SPEAKER_01] samo kršenje je dovoljno.

1362
00:57:44,599 --> 00:57:46,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da nije bilo tako,

1363
00:57:46,960 --> 00:57:47,739
[SPEAKER_01] danas bi imali

1364
00:57:47,739 --> 00:57:49,440
[SPEAKER_01] muškarce obrezane,

1365
00:57:49,440 --> 00:57:49,719
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1366
00:57:49,719 --> 00:57:51,699
[SPEAKER_01] kod židova i muslimana.

1367
00:57:51,699 --> 00:57:52,760
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, vidite,

1368
00:57:52,760 --> 00:57:53,320
[SPEAKER_01] zahvaliti ću tobe,

1369
00:57:53,320 --> 00:57:54,059
[SPEAKER_01] nemamo obrezanja

1370
00:57:54,059 --> 00:57:54,739
[SPEAKER_01] kod muškaraca,

1371
00:57:54,739 --> 00:57:55,280
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, danas,

1372
00:57:55,280 --> 00:57:56,099
[SPEAKER_01] kao što imamo

1373
00:57:56,099 --> 00:57:57,199
[SPEAKER_01] kod židova i muslimana,

1374
00:57:57,199 --> 00:57:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] da se tada,

1375
00:57:58,539 --> 00:57:58,980
[SPEAKER_01] na koncilu,

1376
00:57:58,980 --> 00:57:59,380
[SPEAKER_01] rekao,

1377
00:57:59,380 --> 00:58:00,840
[SPEAKER_01] mora biti taj smjer,

1378
00:58:00,840 --> 00:58:02,820
[SPEAKER_01] danas bi imali tu baštinu.

1379
00:58:02,820 --> 00:58:04,579
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to je crkva koja osluškuje

1380
00:58:04,579 --> 00:58:06,440
[SPEAKER_01] poticaje duha svetoga

1381
00:58:06,440 --> 00:58:07,440
[SPEAKER_01] na razne načine

1382
00:58:07,440 --> 00:58:10,039
[SPEAKER_01] i čini ono što je bitno.

1383
00:58:10,039 --> 00:58:11,860
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da sam vam sve knjige predstavio,

1384
00:58:11,860 --> 00:58:12,119
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1385
00:58:12,119 --> 00:58:12,840
[SPEAKER_01] da ga znamo,

1386
00:58:12,840 --> 00:58:14,840
[SPEAKER_01] nešto nemam ni jednu ovdje pri ruci,

1387
00:58:14,920 --> 00:58:16,400
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, tako je,

1388
00:58:16,400 --> 00:58:16,619
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1389
00:58:16,619 --> 00:58:19,420
[SPEAKER_01] dokumenti crke govore

1390
00:58:19,420 --> 00:58:20,400
[SPEAKER_01] o toj općoj obnovi

1391
00:58:20,400 --> 00:58:21,699
[SPEAKER_01] koji valja prihvatiti

1392
00:58:21,699 --> 00:58:22,940
[SPEAKER_01] i tim smjerom krenuti.

1393
00:58:22,940 --> 00:58:24,880
[SPEAKER_01] A za kraj ćemo onda opet malo se

1394
00:58:24,880 --> 00:58:26,739
[SPEAKER_01] osvrnuti na Scotta Hanna,

1395
00:58:26,739 --> 00:58:30,159
[SPEAKER_01] kako je on otkrio ljepotu

1396
00:58:30,159 --> 00:58:31,920
[SPEAKER_01] katoličke liturgije.

1397
00:58:31,920 --> 00:58:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, protestant je na svetoj misi

1398
00:58:33,800 --> 00:58:35,460
[SPEAKER_01] kao promatrač,

1399
00:58:35,460 --> 00:58:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] pun bijesnoće na katoličku crkvu

1400
00:58:39,000 --> 00:58:41,139
[SPEAKER_01] i na tam put ostane iznenađen

1401
00:58:41,139 --> 00:58:42,860
[SPEAKER_01] slušajući svetu misu.

1402
00:58:44,559 --> 00:58:46,139
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem ovako, u katoličkoj crkvi

1403
00:58:46,139 --> 00:58:48,960
[SPEAKER_01] pisoslovao sam svoje prvoj misi.

1404
00:58:48,960 --> 00:58:51,840
[SPEAKER_01] Uvuko sam se u sražnji dio

1405
00:58:51,840 --> 00:58:53,780
[SPEAKER_01] gdje sam stajao kao stranac,

1406
00:58:53,780 --> 00:58:55,960
[SPEAKER_01] protestantski pastor,

1407
00:58:55,960 --> 00:58:58,119
[SPEAKER_01] neformalno odjeven.

1408
00:58:58,119 --> 00:59:00,800
[SPEAKER_01] U crkvi me dovala znati želja

1409
00:59:00,800 --> 00:59:02,519
[SPEAKER_01] i još uvijek nisam bio siguran

1410
00:59:02,519 --> 00:59:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] radili se o zdravoj znati želji.

1411
00:59:05,000 --> 00:59:08,360
[SPEAKER_01] Proučavajući zapise najranijih kršćana,

1412
00:59:08,360 --> 00:59:10,699
[SPEAKER_01] naišao sam nebrojno puta

1413
00:59:10,699 --> 00:59:12,340
[SPEAKER_01] na pozivanje na liturgiju,

1414
00:59:12,340 --> 00:59:13,619
[SPEAKER_01] euharistiju, žrtvu,

1415
00:59:14,199 --> 00:59:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] za te prve kršćane Biblija,

1416
00:59:16,000 --> 00:59:18,260
[SPEAKER_01] njega koju sam najviše volio,

1417
00:59:18,260 --> 00:59:20,800
[SPEAKER_01] bila nesvatljiva, bez događaja,

1418
00:59:20,800 --> 00:59:23,820
[SPEAKER_01] koji današnji katolici zovu misa.

1419
00:59:23,820 --> 00:59:27,099
[SPEAKER_01] Želio sam razumijeti prve kršćane,

1420
00:59:27,099 --> 00:59:29,679
[SPEAKER_01] međutim nisam imao nikakvoga iskustva

1421
00:59:29,679 --> 00:59:30,679
[SPEAKER_01] s liturgijom.

1422
00:59:31,480 --> 00:59:34,760
[SPEAKER_01] otišao sam u crkvu kao na jedan oblik akademske vježbe.

1423
00:59:35,719 --> 00:59:41,119
[SPEAKER_01] cijelo vrijeme se zakljenjući kako neću niti klečati,

1424
00:59:41,119 --> 00:59:44,079
[SPEAKER_01] niti sljelovati u idolopoklonstvu.

1425
00:59:45,219 --> 00:59:48,900
[SPEAKER_01] sjedio sam u sjeni u klubi na samom kraju te crkve u kripti.

1426
00:59:50,019 --> 00:59:53,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ispred mene je bilo dosta vjernika, muškareca i žena svih uzrasta.

1427
00:59:53,940 --> 00:59:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] Njihov naklon pri ulazku u crkvu ostavio je snažan dojam na mene,

1428
00:59:59,619 --> 01:00:03,639
[SPEAKER_01] kao i njihova očita sabranost u molitvi.

1429
01:00:03,639 --> 01:00:05,739
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad ne znaš k'o te promatra.

1430
01:00:05,739 --> 01:00:09,139
[SPEAKER_01] Možda kroz svoju pobožnost neko dođe do Isusa.

1431
01:00:09,139 --> 01:00:10,380
[SPEAKER_01] Udigo je pobožano.

1432
01:00:10,380 --> 01:00:17,420
[SPEAKER_01] Tad se začelo zvonce, svi su ustali i svećenik je izvišao kroz vrata pored oltara.

1433
01:00:18,800 --> 01:00:20,880
[SPEAKER_01] Nesužavam u sebe, ostal sam sjediti.

1434
01:00:20,880 --> 01:00:27,559
[SPEAKER_01] Godinama su me, kao evangeličkog akavinistu, učili da vjerujem kako je misa

1435
01:00:27,559 --> 01:00:32,559
[SPEAKER_01] najveće svetogrđe, koje ljudsko biće može počiniti.

1436
01:00:32,559 --> 01:00:38,800
[SPEAKER_01] Misa je učili su me obret koji je značio ponovno žrtvovanje Isusa Hrista.

1437
01:00:38,800 --> 01:00:41,179
[SPEAKER_01] Tako sam samo promatrao.

1438
01:00:41,179 --> 01:00:44,800
[SPEAKER_01] Sjedio sam sa otvorenom Biblijom pokraj sebe.

1439
01:00:46,320 --> 01:00:49,280
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se misa međutim nastavljala, nešto me je pogodilo.

1440
01:00:49,280 --> 01:00:52,820
[SPEAKER_01] Moja Biblija nije bila samo pokraj mene.

1441
01:00:52,820 --> 01:00:55,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je bila ispred mene.

1442
01:00:55,699 --> 01:00:58,280
[SPEAKER_01] U riječima sve te mise.

1443
01:00:58,280 --> 01:01:05,340
[SPEAKER_01] Jednoj čini je bilo iz Izaije, drugo iz Salama, treće iz Pavove poslanice.

1444
01:01:05,340 --> 01:01:07,079
[SPEAKER_01] Taj me doželjaj preplavio.

1445
01:01:07,079 --> 01:01:11,219
[SPEAKER_01] Htio sam sve zaustaviti i povikati.

1446
01:01:11,219 --> 01:01:15,239
[SPEAKER_01] Hej, mogu li vam iz Biblije počiniti i objasniti što se događa?

1447
01:01:15,239 --> 01:01:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je izvrsno.

1448
01:01:17,000 --> 01:01:20,219
[SPEAKER_01] Ipak zadržao sam svoje ulogu promatrača.

1449
01:01:20,219 --> 01:01:26,159
[SPEAKER_01] Oslo sam po strani, dok nisam čuo svečenika kako izgovara riječi posvete.

1450
01:01:27,039 --> 01:01:30,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je moje tijelo, ovo je kalež moje krvi.

1451
01:01:30,599 --> 01:01:34,400
[SPEAKER_01] Osjetio sam kako sve moje sumnje nestaju.

1452
01:01:34,400 --> 01:01:38,099
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam vidio svečenika kako podiže bijelu hostiju,

1453
01:01:38,099 --> 01:01:42,719
[SPEAKER_01] osjetio sam kako molitva potiko navire iz moga srca.

1454
01:01:42,719 --> 01:01:48,099
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodi moj i Bog moj, to si zaista ti.

1455
01:01:48,099 --> 01:01:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Od tog trenutka bio sam, kako bi to neki rekli, odsječen.

1456
01:01:53,800 --> 01:01:59,460
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam mogo zamisliti veće uzbuđenje od onoga koje su te riječi u meni pobudile.

1457
01:01:59,460 --> 01:02:04,860
[SPEAKER_01] Doživlja je postao još intenzivniji, samo trenuta kasnije,

1458
01:02:04,860 --> 01:02:07,920
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam čuo kako zajednica izgovara

1459
01:02:07,920 --> 01:02:12,780
[SPEAKER_01] Jaganjče Boži, Jaganjče Boži, Jaganjče Boži.

1460
01:02:12,780 --> 01:02:16,420
[SPEAKER_01] A svečenik odgovara podižući hostiju.

1461
01:02:16,420 --> 01:02:18,539
[SPEAKER_01] Evo Jaganjca Božjega.

1462
01:02:18,539 --> 01:02:21,820
[SPEAKER_01] U vremenu manjem od jedne minute,

1463
01:02:21,820 --> 01:02:25,900
[SPEAKER_01] riječi Jaganjče Boži čule su se četiri puta.

1464
01:02:25,900 --> 01:02:29,699
[SPEAKER_01] Zahvaljujući dugogodišnjem proučavanju Biblije,

1465
01:02:29,699 --> 01:02:32,519
[SPEAKER_01] odmah sam znao gdje se nalazim.

1466
01:02:32,519 --> 01:02:35,679
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam u knjizi Otkrivenja,

1467
01:02:35,679 --> 01:02:43,880
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je Isus nazvan Jaganjcem ne manje od 28 puta u 22 poglavlja.

1468
01:02:44,719 --> 01:02:50,219
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam na svadbenoj gozbi koju Ivan opisuje na kraju posljednje knjige u Bibliji.

1469
01:02:50,219 --> 01:02:52,840
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam pred nebeskim prijestoljem,

1470
01:02:52,840 --> 01:02:55,760
[SPEAKER_01] gdje se Isus vječno slavi kao jaganjac.

1471
01:02:56,460 --> 01:03:00,900
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam bio spreman za ovo, pa ipak bio sam na svetoj misiji.

1472
01:03:00,900 --> 01:03:07,380
[SPEAKER_01] S obnovljenom snagom uronio u svoje proučavanje ranog hršćanstva.

1473
01:03:08,119 --> 01:03:10,719
[SPEAKER_01] I doznao da su najranji biskupi, crpeni otci,

1474
01:03:10,719 --> 01:03:13,280
[SPEAKER_01] doživili to isto otkriće,

1475
01:03:13,280 --> 01:03:15,760
[SPEAKER_01] koje sam ja proželjavao svako jutro.

1476
01:03:15,760 --> 01:03:20,739
[SPEAKER_01] Knjige Otkrivenja smatrali su uključem za razumijevanje liturgije.

1477
01:03:20,739 --> 01:03:25,599
[SPEAKER_01] A liturgiju uključem za razumijevanje knjige Otkrivenja.

1478
01:03:25,599 --> 01:03:27,480
[SPEAKER_01] Otkrivena.

1479
01:03:27,480 --> 01:03:29,400
[SPEAKER_01] Knjiga Otkrivenja.

1480
01:03:29,400 --> 01:03:32,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ne apokalipsa koja zastrašuje ljude,

1481
01:03:32,239 --> 01:03:34,739
[SPEAKER_01] nego knjiga koja otkriva nešto.

1482
01:03:34,739 --> 01:03:36,500
[SPEAKER_01] To je knjiga Otkrivenja.

1483
01:03:36,500 --> 01:03:40,280
[SPEAKER_01] A otkriva da je ta snaga u Isusove žrtvi.

1484
01:03:40,280 --> 01:03:43,860
[SPEAKER_01] Biblijska knjiga koju sam do tada smatrao

1485
01:03:43,860 --> 01:03:45,900
[SPEAKER_01] najzamršenijom knjiga Otkrivenja,

1486
01:03:45,900 --> 01:03:49,360
[SPEAKER_01] osvjetljavala je temelje pojmove moje vjere.

1487
01:03:49,360 --> 01:03:53,679
[SPEAKER_01] Pojam saveza kao svetoga veza Božje obitelji.

1488
01:03:53,679 --> 01:03:56,360
[SPEAKER_01] Povrh toga, radnja koju sam smatrao

1489
01:03:56,360 --> 01:03:58,280
[SPEAKER_01] najveće iz svetogređe misa,

1490
01:03:58,280 --> 01:04:02,519
[SPEAKER_01] pokazala se kao događaj koji je zapečatio Božji savez.

1491
01:04:02,519 --> 01:04:06,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je kalež moje krvi, krvi novoga,

1492
01:04:06,500 --> 01:04:07,780
[SPEAKER_01] i vječnog saveza.

1493
01:04:07,780 --> 01:04:11,699
[SPEAKER_01] Vrtilo mi se od novosti svega ovoga.

1494
01:04:11,699 --> 01:04:15,900
[SPEAKER_01] Godirama sam pokušavao naći smisao knjige Otkrivenja,

1495
01:04:15,900 --> 01:04:20,960
[SPEAKER_01] kao neke vrste kodirane poruke o svošetku svijeta.

1496
01:04:20,960 --> 01:04:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] O bogoštovlju u dalikim nebesima,

1497
01:04:25,079 --> 01:04:28,280
[SPEAKER_01] o nečemu što većina krštena ne može doživjeti

1498
01:04:28,280 --> 01:04:30,179
[SPEAKER_01] dok su još uvijek na zemlji.

1499
01:04:30,179 --> 01:04:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] Dva tjedna nakon svakodnevnog prisustovanja misi

1500
01:04:33,800 --> 01:04:37,980
[SPEAKER_01] iskusio sam kako želim ustaviti za remije liturgije i reći.

1501
01:04:38,639 --> 01:04:43,360
[SPEAKER_01] Hej, svi vi, dopustite da vam pokažem gdje se nalazite u otkrivenju.

1502
01:04:43,360 --> 01:04:47,460
[SPEAKER_01] Okrenite četvrtog poglavlje, redak osmi.

1503
01:04:47,460 --> 01:04:50,559
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ste upravo sada u nebu.

1504
01:04:51,440 --> 01:04:54,219
[SPEAKER_01] Tako evo, skolt hantu mači

1505
01:04:54,219 --> 01:04:59,440
[SPEAKER_01] i završavamo sa ovim dijelom koje imamo ovdje na Zbanovu.

1506
01:04:59,440 --> 01:05:01,440
[SPEAKER_01] Upravo sada u nebu.

1507
01:05:01,440 --> 01:05:06,440
[SPEAKER_01] Crkveni su mi otci pokazali da ovo nije bilo moje otkriće.

1508
01:05:06,440 --> 01:05:10,800
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su o tome pripovjedali prije više od tisuću godina.

1509
01:05:10,800 --> 01:05:15,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam, međutim, bio uvjeren da zaslužujem priznanje

1510
01:05:15,739 --> 01:05:20,239
[SPEAKER_01] za ponovno otkrivanje veze između mise i knjige otkrivenja.

1511
01:05:20,239 --> 01:05:22,139
[SPEAKER_01] On je mislio da je otkrio toplu vodu.

1512
01:05:22,139 --> 01:05:24,099
[SPEAKER_01] A toplu vodu danom prije otkrivena.

1513
01:05:24,099 --> 01:05:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] A sada sam saznao da me i drugi vatkarski sabor prebedu hitrijo.

1514
01:05:31,039 --> 01:05:33,159
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, on se prije jedan glas i on to otkrio.

1515
01:05:33,159 --> 01:05:37,900
[SPEAKER_01] Razmotrite sljedeće riječi iz konstitucije o svetoj liturgiji,

1516
01:05:37,900 --> 01:05:39,360
[SPEAKER_01] a to su riječi ove.

1517
01:05:39,360 --> 01:05:45,239
[SPEAKER_00] U zemaljskoj liturgiji predokusom imamo udjela u onoj nebeskoj

1518
01:05:45,239 --> 01:05:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] koja se slavi u svetom gradu Jeruzalemu,

1519
01:05:48,099 --> 01:05:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] kamo kao putnici težimo gdje z desna Bogu sjedi Krist,

1520
01:05:52,460 --> 01:05:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] služitelj svetišta i pravog šatora sa svim četama nebeske vojske.

1521
01:05:58,039 --> 01:06:00,900
[SPEAKER_00] Pijevamo gospodinu pjesam slave,

1522
01:06:00,900 --> 01:06:03,579
[SPEAKER_00] štujući spomen svih svetih,

1523
01:06:03,579 --> 01:06:06,880
[SPEAKER_00] nadamo se udjoništvu u društvu s njima.

1524
01:06:07,840 --> 01:06:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] Iščekujemo spasitelja, gospodina našega Isusa Hrista,

1525
01:06:11,599 --> 01:06:15,340
[SPEAKER_00] dok se ne pojavi On sam, život naš,

1526
01:06:15,340 --> 01:06:18,900
[SPEAKER_00] te se i mi s njime pojavimo u slavi.

1527
01:06:18,900 --> 01:06:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] I zaključuje Scott Hahn,

1528
01:06:21,199 --> 01:06:23,079
[SPEAKER_01] zastanimo na čas.

1529
01:06:23,079 --> 01:06:24,840
[SPEAKER_01] To je nebo.

1530
01:06:24,840 --> 01:06:26,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, to je misa.

1531
01:06:26,780 --> 01:06:28,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, to je knjiga otkrivenja.

1532
01:06:28,659 --> 01:06:31,139
[SPEAKER_01] Zastanimo još trenutak.

1533
01:06:31,940 --> 01:06:34,019
[SPEAKER_01] To je sve gore navedeno.

1534
01:06:34,019 --> 01:06:35,179
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala lijepo.

